# Admin/Employer Typography Parity

When editing `AdminDashboard` or `EmployerDashboard`, keep typography aligned with Worker dashboard standards:

- Titles/headings -> `Syne` (`h1/h2/h3` or `.font-display`)
- KPI/value emphasis -> `Syne` with clear weight hierarchy
- Body/meta/helper/button labels -> `DM Sans`
- Keep contrast and size rhythm consistent between role dashboards
- Avoid introducing additional font families or one-off font overrides
